create index.html and app.js

    create alert and console in body tag in index.html


Instead of write alert and console in body tag in index.html,
    I put it inside the app.js, 

Have shortcut, 'ctrl' + 'space' in the src of script tag in index.html, it will show the app.js file, 
    then I select it and it will link the app.js to index.html, so when I open the index.html in 
    live server, it will run the code in app.js and show the alert and console log.      
